Character

The character model.

  • {string} id - The id of the character
  • {string} name - The name of the character
  • {CharPosition} position - The position of the character
  • {LevelKeyCollection} keys - The keys which the character has at the moment
  • {LevelHistoryCollection} histories - The histories of the levels in the current floor
  • {PlayingState} playingState - The playing state of the last level
  • {LevelLockCollection} locks - The locks statuses of the levels in the current floor

Character represents heros like Ma, Ellen, Emma.
